thread.title: Maria

author: Maria
title: Maria
text: Loved shopping with them! Ordered from Ireland - prices are substantially cheaper on everything compared to Irish retailers. Plus, Baby Garage has ALL the options for the Cybex Priam (can pick wheels, base, seat). Delivery was quick and everything arrived in perfect condition. I am very pleased! Will be back! Oh! And the Customer support answered all my questions via email that I had about the product prior to purchasing in a fast and professional manner!
